  <h2>How to book</h2>

  <h3>By telephone</h3>
  <p>Call us on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a> from 08:00, Monday to Friday. Our reception team will help you find the most appropriate appointment.</p>

  <h3>Online via Patient Access</h3>
  <p>If you are registered with Patient Access, you can book some appointments online at any time.</p>
